Release Notes
All Credit to fenyesk who created the XGBoost. I converted this to a strategy and removed the alerts since that was redundant and removed the long and short signals because the trades show up so also redundant and I plan on using this for the Leap competition. Feel free to copy this but make sure to give credit to fenyesk
Release Notes
Added barstate.isconfirmed to help reduce the number of alerts when to buy and sell.
Release Notes
Fix to use strategy strategy.position_size instead of current_pos. Hopefully this will reduce the false positives?
Release Notes
Fixed the ta.crossunder and ta.crossover The "ta.crossunder()" call inside the conditional expression might not execute on every bar, which can cause inconsistent calculations because the function depends on historical results. For consistency, assign the call's result to a global variable and use that variable in the expression instead
